{"tid":1887683,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"香港搞租車有冇得諗","createTime":"2020-02-19T17:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T12:03:16.000Z","uid":326792,"like":1,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"c3c953c88adb6a93ca93d8c51e886ea179e92715","tid":1887683,"uid":326792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:01:08.000Z","msg":"小弟本身有架車 揸左幾年 當年都係二手買返黎<br />\n<br />\n忽發其想 同朋友登記間公司買幾架二手車租俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道保險可能好貴同埋有一定風險<br />\n稍一不慎就可能令自己或者人地負上好大責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定會搞清楚啲保險先開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問過下普通車保一般都唔包租俾人<br />\n好似應該要用商業，甚至寫到明「租賃」既車保?<br />\n但呢方面小弟搵到既資料比較少，價錢都唔太肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有保險／車房既朋友方便既話 希望可以俾啲意見小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現階段想上黎睇下大家對「喺香港租車揸」有幾大興趣<br />\n如果有興趣既，方便既話可以留低牌齡做個統計，睇下可唔可行<br />\n<br />\n有時間既ching不妨填埋以下呢個問卷俾啲意見我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/fLGnU77vSx4hDsMG7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FfLGnU77vSx4hDsMG7&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5Ou9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=aa90b4e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/fLGnU77vSx4hDsMG7</a> <br />\n<br />\n多謝晒您地入黎俾意見同花時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n萬分感激"},{"pid":"0bf800afbc496f48b83de11696c5ac17874f0141","tid":1887683,"uid":147871,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"ci