好<br />\n<br />\n如果keep住租多幾日嘅，又要自己煩泊車<br />\n<br />\n好難抉擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"出租費邊有肉食架<br />\n不嬲都係係賺不明車損然後屈返一筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:21:39.000Z","msg":"都聽過坊間好多係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平平地10年入門車 應該都賺到既 又唔係諗住發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係驚保險好貴同冇人租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f9c056c70d893f99673c5396e41b8f1570f873","tid":1887683,"uid":226488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:33:44.000Z","msg":"有冇得做真係唔知<br />\n但拍賣網上有唔少盤<br />\n<br />\n利申: 自己有車冇諗過租"},{"pid":"2c17ae48d190dc8b63eecc51c2e40e3924d2fecd","tid":1887683,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:55:00.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n<a href=\"http://Carshare.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FCarshare.hk&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5Ou9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=2a258951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Carshare.hk</a> 玩左幾年, 而家執埋<br />\n仲有單出名嘅皮車皮壞車新聞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160309/00176_081.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160309%2F00176_081.html&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5Ou9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=d0df2b98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20160309/00176_081.html</a><br />\n<br />\n已經前車可鑑ed, 你柒下柒下咩都唔知去搞實仲死得快過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1395a3501173fb33d241879b55fe043b92561e","tid":1887683,"uid":50212,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T17:59:35.000Z","msg":"好簡單咁講<br />\n有得做仲等你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas